text: Velyki Makary () is a village in Yavoriv Raion, Lviv Oblast, Ukraine. The town was founded in 1592, with an area of 0.56 square kilometers and an elevation of 268 meters. As of the 2001 census, the population was 206. == References == * Official Information (Ukrainian) * Weather in the town of Velyki Makary (Ukrainian) * Map of Velyki Makary Category:Villages in Yavoriv Raion
